  "text": "For the case of beams subjected to both torsion and shear, a modified potential stress approach has been proposed in [CITATION_1] , superimposing the stress field generated by the shear forces applied at the flexure center and the stress field due to pure torsion. The two fields are determined by the solution of two Neumann problems and three Dirichlet problems,",
